name: J-Sei Meals on Wheels
description: J-Sei provides culturally appropriate Japanese-style home-delivered meals to seniors in Alameda County, honoring cultural food traditions while ensuring nutrition and social connection.
fullDescription: J-Sei provides culturally appropriate Japanese-style home-delivered meals to seniors in Alameda County, honoring cultural food traditions while ensuring nutrition and social connection.
whatTheyOffer:
- Japanese-style hot meals delivered to your home
- Culturally appropriate menu
- Available for seniors 60+ who have difficulty leaving home
- Suggested donation, but never denied for inability to pay
- Friendly check-ins with each delivery
howToGetIt: Call J-Sei to apply. You must be 60+ and have difficulty leaving your home to prepare or obtain food. Staff will assess eligibility and set up meal deliveries.
keywords: J-Sei, Japanese meals, Asian senior, culturally appropriate, home delivered meals, senior food, Alameda County, ethnic food
